{"tid":2033713,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想班藍絲bno去英國嘅入嚟","createTime":"2020-05-24T22:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T15:22:07.000Z","uid":281584,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"de8a703fef636097437d0163e6e2da4291a1f9c2","tid":2033713,"uid":281584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T22:39:20.000Z","msg":"同1997年7月1號前出世班藍絲講,手足父母除外<br />\n有BNO=偽藍<br />\n去英國=做二等公民<br />\n<br />\n退出bno form(從未申請bno亦適用,需要出世紙)<br />\n<a href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/795221/form-rn-04-2019.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.publishing.service.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fuploads%2Fsystem%2Fuploads%2Fattachment_data%2Ffile%2F795221%2Fform-rn-04-2019.pdf&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMkUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=b786e26f\" target=\"_blank\">https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/795221/form-rn-04-2019.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n所需文件<br />\n1.退出bno form<br />\n2.bno 不論過期與否 or  出世紙<br />\n3.英國以外passport（影印本唔知得唔得) or 政府文件能証明有英國以外國箱<br />\n<br />\n寄去<br />\nDepartment 1<br />\nUKVI<br />\nThe Capital<br />\nNew Hall Place<br />\nLiverpool<br />\nL3 9PP. <br />\n<br />\n詳細說明<br />\n<a href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/788693/Guide_RN__1_.PDF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.publishing.service.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fuploads%2Fsystem%2Fuploads%2Fattachment_data%2Ffile%2F788693%2FGuide_RN__1_.PDF&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMkUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=3d18e276\" target=\"_blank\">https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/788693/Guide_RN__1_.PDF</a><br />\n<br />\n如有錯漏請指正"},{"pid":"945175c3c1b560892db8b2ef719c7a3a71567c5a","tid":2033713,"uid":343977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T22:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f4d9cc84c9797e12f7a4103a67759e190f49db","tid":2033713,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T22:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9bf2fd4affd676fbcc3532b7a81ff008c53fbe","tid":2033713,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T23:09:16.000Z","msg":"收皮啦P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7922542c2272e79ada3159c5970c9a093984f29a","tid":2033713,"uid":258377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:33:41.000Z","msg":"有無人幫689 &amp; 777 填form<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa5ec89354980a0cd81298ca4dd3d884c5f0296","tid":2033713,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BNO平權正視聽</span></span><br />\n連登一向有大量風向L、放負L，睇到BNO平權消息就用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>割97後等風向挑撥離間</strong></span>，大家上連登請帶埋個腦。<br />\n<br />\n我從六月開始打英國戰線，希望嚮呢度講幾句。<br />\n第一，BNO平權唔會割97後，因為我地一向都係爭取救<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">BNO及其後代</span></strong>。，除非你係雙非，否則幾乎一定會受惠。<br />\n第二，BNO平權絕對係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同美國行動有關係</strong></span>，故此毫無疑問就係一個救手足之舉，甚至可能與<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">軍事撤僑</span></strong>有關。<br />\n第三，BNO平到權主要唔係用包機包船黎接香港人去英國，亦都冇咩可能會接，畢竟人數太多。平到權最大重點係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>BNO變正式英國國民，中共逼害英國國民嘅話，英國以至美國就有理由做野</strong></span>。<br />\n第四，BNO平權估計會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寬鬆處理，英屬香港人（BOTC、BDTC、CUKC）無BNO或者已經過期應該都ok</span></strong>。因為英國情報已經判斷香港情況差到似烏干達難民。<br />\n第五，BNO平權大家可以更加無後顧之憂，因為將來要良民證黎移民，可以向英國當局申請。"},{"pid":"e647d423c955d12b8eb185a92d494639aee0d07d","tid":2033713,"uid":358640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:08:25.000Z","msg":"BNO平權有助香港建立海外屬地 黃色經濟圈全球化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2034495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2034495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"df360c4b13594898c39c2fdb70555f184217e2e4","tid":2033713,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efa5ec89354980a0cd81298ca4dd3d884c5f0296","tid":2033713,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BNO平權正視聽</span></span><br />\n連登一向有大量風向L、放負L，睇到BNO平權消息就用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>割97後等風向挑撥離間</strong></span>，大家上連登請帶埋個腦。<br />\n<br />\n我從六月開始打英國戰線，希望嚮呢度講幾句。<br />\n第一，BNO平權唔會割97後，因為我地一向都係爭取救<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">BNO及其後代</span></strong>。，除非你係雙非，否則幾乎一定會受惠。<br />\n第二，BNO平權絕對係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同美國行動有關係</strong></span>，故此毫無疑問就係一個救手足之舉，甚至可能與<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">軍事撤僑</span></strong>有關。<br />\n第三，BNO平到權主要唔係用包機包船黎接香港人去英國，亦都冇咩可能會接，畢竟人數太多。平到權最大重點係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>BNO變正式英國國民，中共逼害英國國民嘅話，英國以至美國就有理由做野</strong></span>。<br />\n第四，BNO平權估計會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寬鬆處理，英屬香港人（BOTC、BDTC、CUKC）無BNO或者已經過期應該都ok</span></strong>。因為英國情報已經判斷香港情況差到似烏干達難民。<br />\n第五，BNO平權大家可以更加無後顧之憂，因為將來要良民證黎移民，可以向英國當局申請。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:22:07.000Z","msg":"但問題係 唔可以俾班藍屍壞事做盡都過到英國！"}]}